### Description

Hi there,

Recently I am reinstalling nvim in my Linux machine. I am working on C code and nvim lsp shows a strange behavior, every symbol is showing twice as screenshot below

<img width="1020" height="570" alt="Image" src="https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/38183509-09b9-4d35-b7a8-4180b43dae46" />

